    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your<strong> spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
