    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> dried oregano</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
