      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>chicken Milanese</strong> thinly on a clean board</p><p>Serve the <strong>spaghetti pomodoro </strong>topped with the<strong> sliced chicken Milanese </strong>and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
